comment:
* Internal class used to gather statistics on the RWLock.
     * @hide Only a subset of ICU is exposed in Android

variables.name: _rc
variables.comment: * Number of times read access granted (read count).

variables.name: _mrc
variables.comment: * Number of times concurrent read access granted (multiple read count).

variables.name: _wc
variables.comment: * Number of times write access granted (writer count).

variables.name: _wwc
variables.comment: * Number of times blocked for write (waiting writer count).

methods.name: public String toString()
methods.comment: * Return a string listing all the stats.
